about.summary: Simple library to encode/decode DNS wire-format packets

name: dnslib
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "dnslib" %}
{% set version = "0.9.10" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: "https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz"
  sha256: 666bf55274a630a2925411c4ea9ca724529299bbe70f91979ad99c72c5e5099e

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - dnslib

about:
  home: "http://bitbucket.org/paulc/dnslib/"
  license: "BSD-2-Clause"
  license_family: "BSD"
  license_file: "LICENSE"
  summary: "Simple library to encode/decode DNS wire-format packets"
  doc_url: "https://pypi.org/project/dnslib/"
  dev_url: "https://bitbucket.org/paulc/dnslib/src/default/"

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - mwilson8
    - oblute
    - benhuff
